{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"83dd7aaf-676b-43ee-95a8-4e805b17f705","content":"Here's what you need:\n\n### Environment Variables\n\nSet these on your container to enable automatic crash dump collection via `createdump`:\n\n| Variable | Value | Purpose |\n|---|---|---|\n| `DOTNET_DbgEnableMiniDump` | `1` | Enable automatic dump on crash |\n| `DOTNET_DbgMiniDumpType` | `4` | Full dump with heap (`MiniDumpWithFullMemory`) |\n| `DOTNET_DbgMiniDumpName` | `/tmp/dumps/coredump.%p.%t` | Dump path (`%p`=PID, `%t`=timestamp) |\n| `DOTNET_DbgCreatedumpPath` | `/opt/tools/createdump` | Custom createdump location |\n\n### Pod Spec Changes\n\n```yaml\napiVersion: v1\nkind: Pod\nmetadata:\n  name: my-nativeaot-app\nspec:\n  containers:\n  - name: app\n    image: my-app:latest\n    env:\n    - name: DOTNET_DbgEnableMiniDump\n      value: \"1\"\n    - name: DOTNET_DbgMiniDumpType\n      value: \"4\"\n    - name: DOTNET_DbgMiniDumpName\n      value: \"/tmp/dumps/coredump.%p.%t\"\n    - name: DOTNET_DbgCreatedumpPath\n      value: \"/opt/tools/createdump\"\n    volumeMounts:\n    - name: dump-volume\n      mountPath: /tmp/dumps\n    securityContext:\n      capabilities:\n        add:\n        - SYS_PTRACE          # required for createdump to attach\n  volumes:\n  - name: dump-volume\n    emptyDir:\n      sizeLimit: 4Gi          # adjust to expected dump size\n```\n\n### Key notes\n\n- **`SYS_PTRACE`** is required — `createdump` uses `ptrace` to read process memory.\n- **`emptyDir`** keeps dumps on the node. Swap to a **PersistentVolumeClaim** if you need dumps to survive pod restarts.\n- **Dump types**: `1`=Normal, `2`=WithPrivateReadWriteMemory, `3`=FilterTriage, `4`=Full. Use `4` for NativeAOT since managed heap metadata is harder to reconstruct.\n- Set `DOTNET_DbgCreateDumpDiagnostics=1` temporarily if you need to debug the dump collection itself.","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"2065489b-93ba-457c-88de-cfb611cadd5c","outputTokens":617,"requestId":"2C51:1801E:15590D5:183AFCC:69F94C50"},"id":"0b252a44-e54b-4ed1-8644-9b5342f0613e","timestamp":"2026-05-05T01:48:11.428Z","parentId":"308f8038-62de-44c0-b784-335a7beae1a3"}
